								<node id="editorData">
									<children>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="NOTE: No Love interest, , [GERRY] From the position of Mizora touching the player chin (her leaning over and player sitting - they both get up in a more relaxed and intimate manner to standing positions facing each other. The flames surrounding the player and Mizora are extinguished. Mizora turns roughly 90 degrees to the right and takes a few steps forward -  A diabolical circle appears under Mizora and she jauntily waves at the Player as she descends into it." />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="Attitude" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Default" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="NOTE: No Love interest&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;[GERRY+Latino] From the position of Mizora touching the player chin (her leaning over and player sitting - she stands up. Mizora turns roughly 90 degrees to the right and takes a few steps forward -  A diabolical circle appears under Mizora and she jauntily waves at the Player as she descends into it.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;JLatino: Cut &quot;The flames surrounding the player and Mizora are extinguished.&quot; and we leave the player on the ground." />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicObjects" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CustomCineArtKeysPresent" />
