											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[AMN][GUS-239513] Mizora walks around the Player (on their left side), looking down at them as she walks past. She stops in front of the Player. Her back is facing them as she talks about delighting in her experience., , As she is about to finish her line, she turns around to face the player. Forms a standard Bronze staging., , NOTE: Player is still seated and naked/in their underwear." />
