											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[GERRY][AMN][GUS-239513] Mizora saunters/ sashays towards the Player. She bends over and reaches out with her right hand to touch the Player's chin in an intimate gesture., , As she finishes the line, she looks up and to the right to where the love interest is (who is positioned offscreen), , Player hurriedly draws back from Mizora and scurries to their feet after being discovered by love interest., Mizora straightens up, withdraws her hand and turns to face Player's love interest" />
